Package: binaryRL
Version: 0.7.9
Title: Reinforcement Learning tools for Two-Alternative Forced Choice tasks
Description:
  This package provides tools for building reinforcement learning models
  for Two-Alternative Forced Choice tasks, commonly used in
  psychological research. It simplifies model construction, allowing
  users to define models using if-else statements. The package provides tools 
  for building, fitting, and recovering reinforcement learning models.
